{"tid":1478490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人話818有鬼，點算？","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T12:16:09.000Z","uid":303304,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e6971f4313b5db827b737c755fc7556f6820dc43","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">先旨聲明：極不同意主動捉鬼</span></span><br />\n近日極多人流傳又fucking刀手，又武警，又解放軍咁嚟造鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先大家一定要認清一個事實，近日啲狗嘅鬼見左光，而且成為把柄，所以估計短期內啲鬼都唔會再係啲狗做，應該都係中央派落嚟<br />\n咁點算呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記得咪主動捉鬼</span><br />\n但係，假如你聽到隔離嗰個講普通話，或者唔鹹唔淡嘅廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就簡單，只要打開你個手機，影撚住佢，然後叫佢講<span style=\"color: red;\">「平反六四」</span><span style=\"color: red;\">「維尼習帝」「支持新疆獨立」</span>等大陸口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢唔肯講，咁都有99%係鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以大聲叫定記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪亂咁除人哋啲口罩</span></span>，萬一係手足就捉蟲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，有記者嘅話就咪打佢哋，攞光環，不過如果冇記者喎，就就乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話唔俾你衝，不過衝嘅就一定要係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49740fcfa09abd4e783eaaed2b75ad008b8d41f7","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"973e874d4973688fd8eaeef86a0377f2734b1026","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"606cb4e78d3b6ea2cff3e6f396eef7439805cac8","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6348c14a49697cb9483d3f67258d0322850e1583","tid":1478490,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7010779e31120f387d9aa07032a451a34242d49c","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"97892f7455a192fc3765b21f24a8adea4baa0463","tid":1478490,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"憑直覺行事<br />\n<br />\n鬼好明顯"},{"pid":"c2b70f9a283e56a4803575aa4c9e56a15944475a","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9ae54e72eb8afc1f3139c1575c0c8d53ac269839","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97892f7455a192fc3765b21f24a8adea4baa0463","tid":1478490,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"憑直覺行事<br />\n<br />\n鬼好明顯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"啱，最緊要咪主動捉鬼，前線啲手足做野好講信任"},{"pid":"5923463c3ad377184812e001867065b1e284a0f7","tid":1478490,"uid":189377,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:11:13.000Z","msg"