mal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢唔肯講，咁都有99%係鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以大聲叫定記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪亂咁除人哋啲口罩</span></span>，萬一係手足就捉蟲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，有記者嘅話就咪打佢哋，攞光環，不過如果冇記者喎，就就乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話唔俾你衝，不過衝嘅就一定要係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要和平理性非暴力, 不要煽動他人, 又不要被他人煽動<br />\n做好自己, 做好高質香港人, 每個人都係甘地.和平主義者<br />\n共同迎接聯合國出手.</span>"},{"pid":"2879bf41dc7f9e651ff080f3ed7f87734f8045d1","tid":1478490,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"只要人夠多，就唔會怕鬼"},{"pid":"282c83c112e10801c8133a27b64a893eaee16a9f","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2879bf41dc7f9e651ff080f3ed7f87734f8045d1","tid":1478490,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"只要人夠多，就唔會怕鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"啱，圍鳩佢"},{"pid":"b2329e4fc6e53c49b5d1590d8ee38edb99ebc928","tid":1478490,"uid":193040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122674077c9f70d9ef0eb36d22321f66adb2c3e3","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislik