/>\n高汁片轉發<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"9584a5ad99a09d339bf74326f59c2f0316d80d42","tid":1478490,"uid":56062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6971f4313b5db827b737c755fc7556f6820dc43","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:07:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">先旨聲明：極不同意主動捉鬼</span></span><br />\n近日極多人流傳又fucking刀手，又武警，又解放軍咁嚟造鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先大家一定要認清一個事實，近日啲狗嘅鬼見左光，而且成為把柄，所以估計短期內啲鬼都唔會再係啲狗做，應該都係中央派落嚟<br />\n咁點算呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記得咪主動捉鬼</span><br />\n但係，假如你聽到隔離嗰個講普通話，或者唔鹹唔淡嘅廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就簡單，只要打開你個手機，影撚住佢，然後叫佢講<span style=\"color: red;\">「平反六四」</span><span style=\"color: red;\">「維尼習帝」「支持新疆獨立」</span>等大陸口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢唔肯講，咁都有99%係鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以大聲叫定記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪亂咁除人哋啲口罩</span></span>，萬一係手足就捉蟲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，有記者嘅話就咪打佢哋，攞光環，不過如果冇記者喎，就就乜都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話唔俾你衝，不過衝嘅就一定要係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:12:51.000Z","msg":"大陸人大陸記者拍野咪比佢拍囉<br />\n記得印定d唔可以起大陸登報的標語<br />\ne.g. 京A88519,  我們支持香港警察我們今天可以上街了， 平反武漢武力震壓，等<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察混入黎發現左，唔洗打，反而要歡呼佢肯一齊黎光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n如果有人真係打人想殺人，呢d咁過分違反人權嘅野，咁緊係一齊㩒住佢啦。<br />\nWe are against the system, not any individual. <br />\n<br />\n因果由國，容港治己，<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"7e43031873edc700f1a69a9045bc8dd96bf3b345","tid":1478490,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:16:49.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf4b98088cd47ed82dff2ddf1a0b9221b97aa153","tid":1478490,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:37:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfam93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFfam93.jpg&h=f46c0dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n'If not us, <strong>WHO</strong>? <br />\nIf not now, <strong>WHEN</strong>?'<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">RIGHT THE WRONG, FREE HONG KONG</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">817宋皇臺 <br />\n818維園</span></span><br />\n<br />\n試問誰還未發聲<br />\n都捨我其誰<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>衛我城</strong></span><br />\n天生有權還有心可作主<br />\n誰要認命噤聲</div>"},{"pid":"8eabb48d76dfac254c7bf2e0ec99602c5a09cf07","tid":1478490,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:55:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e2c80b46ff191f1661576c579fc15a0cc1863ed","tid":1478490,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2